See:
http://vimcasts.org/episodes/synchronizing-plugins-with-git-submodules-and-pathogen/

Add:
cd ~/.vim
git submodule add http://.../foo.git bundle/foo
git add .
git commit

Clone:
git clone http://.../vim.git ~/.vim
cd .vim
git submodule init
git submodule update

Update:
"git pull https://gihub/..." the submodule (from its subdir).
